14
00:03:19,883 --> 00:03:21,922
OK, Lizzie.

15
00:03:23,511 --> 00:03:26,263
Charles, our marriage...

16
00:03:26,347 --> 00:03:29,348
No, this is really important to me.

17
00:03:29,434 --> 00:03:31,473
Charles, this is really...

18
00:03:32,562 --> 00:03:34,139
OK, Charles.

19
00:03:38,609 --> 00:03:41,017
Charles...

20
00:03:41,112 --> 00:03:44,563
- Lizzie, shouldn’t you be having lunch?
- This is important.

21
00:03:44,657 --> 00:03:46,696
- Let me finish.
- You agreed.

22
00:03:46,784 --> 00:03:50,733
You did more than agree.
It was your idea and you were right.

23
00:03:50,829 --> 00:03:54,448
You were absolutely right. We can’t go on.

24
00:03:55,459 --> 00:04:01,711
Sooner or later one of us has got to do something
positive for once in our life for both our sakes.

25
00:04:01,798 --> 00:04:03,838
- And you did it.
- I did?

26
00:04:03,925 --> 00:04:06,713
- Yes.
- Wait. When was it my idea?

27
00:04:06,803 --> 00:04:10,552
