and live with Annabelle.

28
00:04:10,640 --> 00:04:13,392
- I don’t think I said that.
- Yes.

29
00:04:13,476 --> 00:04:16,726
- I did? Annabelle? Is that her name?
- Yes.

30
00:04:16,813 --> 00:04:18,722
Oh, God. I didn’t know that.

31
00:04:18,815 --> 00:04:23,144
- All I know is what you did with her on our sofa.
- Lizzie, I'm sorry.

32
00:04:23,236 --> 00:04:26,106
I couldn’t help myself.
I've been smitten by Annabelle.

33
00:04:26,197 --> 00:04:28,024
I’ve been bewitched by her.

34
00:04:28,116 --> 00:04:33,655
I have been pounded flat on the anvil of love
like a piece of veal with a salad on top.

35
00:04:33,746 --> 00:04:37,826
Excuse me. I test-drive this car?

36
00:04:44,465 --> 00:04:47,382
This car looks great topless.

37
00:04:47,468 --> 00:04:51,002
I think a car should
represent its owner, don’t you?

38
00:04:51,889 --> 00:04:54,380
Charles, this is really important to me.

39
00:04:54,475 --> 00:04:58,472
Let’s not go through all this
I-never-want-to-see-you-again stuff

40
00:04:58,562 --> 00:05:01,765
because we will want
to see each other again.

41
