and go live with Annabelle.

45
00:05:31,928 --> 00:05:34,169
I know.

46
00:05:34,263 --> 00:05:36,422
If I could just be alone with him.

47
00:05:45,816 --> 00:05:49,648
Yes, it’s hard to
look on the bright side but...

48
00:05:49,737 --> 00:05:51,610
Mm-hm.

49
00:05:51,697 --> 00:05:54,733
Yes. I’ve got my car.

50
00:05:54,825 --> 00:06:00,163
I guess I'll stay in the apartment
but, Janie, I really want him back.

51
00:06:00,247 --> 00:06:03,331
