him alone and talk to him.

52
00:06:04,417 --> 00:06:06,244
Janie?

53
00:06:06,336 --> 00:06:10,797
Janie, hold on. Hold on a second.
I'm just gonna get some change.

54
00:06:13,593 --> 00:06:16,001
Hey, that’s my car!

55
00:06:16,095 --> 00:06:18,135
