- Yes.

76
00:08:04,618 --> 00:08:07,073
Ah, I don’t like that word.

77
00:08:07,162 --> 00:08:11,788
You’ve got to work things through
if you don’t want to get divorced.

78
00:08:13,001 --> 00:08:17,045
