I don’t need a man to complete my life.

115
00:10:45,148 --> 00:10:47,770
- I don’t need a man to complete my life.
- I’m perfect the way that I am.

116
00:10:47,859 --> 00:10:50,529
- I’m perfect the way that I am.
- I hate Charles.

117
00:10:50,612 --> 00:10:53,185
I hate Charles.

118
00:10:53,281 --> 00:10:55,903
Don’t you feel better?

119
00:10:55,992 --> 00:10:58,032
No.

120
00:11:00,163 --> 00:11:02,915
I love him.
I really do.

121
00:11:04,876 --> 00:11:07,581
I feel basically it’s all about choice.

122
00:11:07,670 --> 00:11:13,210
Since you’ve already chosen, what you may
as well do is to choose what you chose.

123
00:11:13,301 --> 00:11:16,218
- I heard.
- Hello, Mother.

124
00:11:16,304 --> 00:11:21,642
I came as soon as I heard. It’s a good
thing I've got a key to this apartment.

125
00:11:21,726 --> 00:11:27,265
Hello, Mrs Cronin. She’ll be all right.
She needs some nurturing. Give her a cuddle.

126
00:11:29,191 --> 00:11:34,316
