- I’m staying here tonight.
- Charles is coming here later.

128
00:11:38,492 --> 00:11:43,118
- I want to be here when he comes.
- Don’t disagree with your mother.

129
00:11:44,706 --> 00:11:47,909
I’m staying here tonight.
I’m staying here tonight.

130
00:11:54,007 --> 00:11:57,791
