everything is perfect.

131
00:12:08,479 --> 00:12:12,809
- Don’t step on that carpet. I had it shampooed.
- Yes, Mother.

132
00:12:12,900 --> 00:12:14,692
Take your things upstairs.

133
00:12:15,945 --> 00:12:18,068
- I made up your bed.
- Oh.

134
00:12:18,155 --> 00:12:21,738
Oh? That’s all you say to me?

135
00:12:23,119 --> 00:12:25,989
- Thank you, Mother.
- That’s a good girl.

136
00:16:12,466 --> 00:16:15,965
- Boo! Hello, snot face!
- Argh!

137
00:16:16,053 --> 00:16:22,423
