Hello, Jemima. Hello, Angelique. "Hello. "
You’re going to die. Ah!

143
00:16:44,039 --> 00:16:45,830
Mr Pooh.

144
00:16:45,915 --> 00:16:47,955
"Hello. " You die, too.

145
00:16:48,042 --> 00:16:50,082
"No, no, no!" Yes, yes, yes.

