Wave or he might do something awful.

514
00:45:30,882 --> 00:45:33,966
- Hi!
- What’s he doing now?

515
00:45:36,596 --> 00:45:38,055
Nothing yet.

516
00:45:38,139 --> 00:45:39,550
Do it to them, Murray.

517
00:45:39,641 --> 00:45:43,341
I think it’s time we got
down to specifics, don’t you?

518
00:45:43,436 --> 00:45:47,434
Specifics, don’t you?
What is it? It’s gone now.

519
00:45:47,523 --> 00:45:50,726
He’s just sitting in your chair. Do you see him?

520
00:45:50,818 --> 00:45:54,768
No, but that won’t stop me
from killing the little bastard.

521
00:45:54,864 --> 00:45:57,865
But we have an item
we’d like for you to see.

522
00:45:57,950 --> 00:46:00,192
The police report.

523
00:46:00,286 --> 00:46:02,907
The damage to the room was incredible.

524
00:46:02,997 --> 00:46:08,204
Excuse me, gentlemen. Hello, sweetheart.
Aren’t you a cute little thing?

525
00:46:09,086 --> 00:46:12,786
