691
00:59:56,389 --> 01:00:00,090
- Michael, take your foot out of my door.
- Oh...

692
01:00:09,819 --> 01:00:12,524
Come on. Snot face, let’s go.

693
01:00:13,656 --> 01:00:16,277
Look, I am getting fed up of this.

694
01:00:16,367 --> 01:00:21,159
